  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee or oil in a large saucepan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onion and sauté until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add ginger and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add tomato and sauté for 2 minutes.",
    "Add curry powder and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add Australian rice krispies and stir to coat with spices.",
    "Add coconut milk and water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 18-20 minutes or until the liquid is fully absorbed.",
    "Fluff the biryani with a fork and season with salt to taste."
